# A3: GM Server-saves with the server unreachable (engine exit 3) must diagnose — the pre-A3
# code showed "No server saves for <game>" (the exact 22:31 Smart Pro line).
desc Game Manager: Server saves with engine rc=3 -> diagnose, never "No server saves"
config paired
seeded
sdfile+ Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Zelda.gba
pick 0|Game Manager
pick 0|Game Boy Advance (GBA)
pick 0|✓ Zelda.gba
pick 0|Server saves
pick 2|
engine 3|
expect_exit 0
expect_trace_absent PRES timeout=3 msg='No server saves for ✓ Zelda.gba'
expect_log err: Couldn't reach your server - check the server or your connection, then retry
